OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain will
OL,6,Fspread northeast during this evening
OL,7,Fand in the early hours. Drier weather
OL,8,Fdeveloping later in the night. Strong
OL,9,Fsouthwesterly winds along the northern
OL,10,FArgyll coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FIt will be mild and cloudy
OL,13,Fthroughout the day. Mostly dry for
OL,14,Fgreater Glasgow and Ayrshire, but
OL,15,Foutbreaks of rain for Argyll and the
OL,16,FIsles, heavy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
